text: Senayangba Chubatoshi Jamir (born 17 October 1931"S.C. Jamir sworn in Maharashtra Governor" , PTI (The Hindu), 19 July 2008.) is an Indian politician. He was the Governor of Odisha from 2013 to 2018. He was the Chief Minister of Nagaland, Governor of Maharashtra, Governor of Gujarat, Governor of Goa and Governor of Odisha. Jamir is a member of the Indian National Congress. He was born in Ungma, Nagaland. ==References== Category:1931 births Category:Living people Category:Governors of Goa Category:Governors of Gujarat Category:Governors of Maharashtra Category:Governors of Odisha
